title: NZ Lifestyle Block - May 2014
description:
NZ Lifestyle Block - May 2014

92 Pages | True PDF | English | 17 MB 


NZ Lifestyle Block provides you with practical information for running a successful lifestyle block or small farm, with information on specialist livestock, organic gardening and orchards, DIY power, how to be self-sufficient, create great food from your endeavours, and lots of inspiring examples of people living on small blocks.
